price: 69. Tuurna waxa ku jira gacantaaada midig! Waxay liqi waxay sameeyeen, waxa ay sameeyeen waa uun tab sixirrow, mana liibaano sixirrow meeluu yimaadaba.
arabic: وَأَلۡقِ مَا فِي يَمِينِكَ تَلۡقَفۡ مَا صَنَعُوٓاْۖ إِنَّمَا صَنَعُواْ كَيۡدُ سَٰحِرٖۖ وَلَا يُفۡلِحُ ٱلسَّاحِرُ حَيۡثُ أَتَىٰ

version.title: Somali translation - Jacob
version.description: Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur'an into the Somali language, translated by Abdullah Hasan Jacob.
